{"tid":398932,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[味噌醬]去完日本，買左呢隻醬返香港，我返唔到轉頭","createTime":"2017-09-13T14:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T06:49:20.000Z","uid":74778,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f8562e0f2d31bbf2d56f42df50c75b7f8ffc7da","tid":398932,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/13/215944_e116de268e8232174df1fcd840d16fbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F215944_e116de268e8232174df1fcd840d16fbe.jpg&h=b908812b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家食曬好空虛<br />\n<br />\n阿媽煮求其放湯，煮麵、粉絲、豆腐、蛋、雞肉、菜，已經好味到癲。<br />\n<br />\n宜家食曬，我叫d去日本既朋友幫我買，<br />\n<br />\n阿媽話香港超巿都有，有無巴絲見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1961ea787a1db0df0e49b843f2a827f079cbd1","tid":398932,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:17:58.000Z","msg":"香港超巿都有"},{"pid":"2fe606e6a58b9459c10673ab45a55a3a43f49c36","tid":398932,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:22:10.000Z","msg":"味增?"},{"pid":"411fc6faec67384696bfc1b515574451ab429428","tid":398932,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:35:45.000Z","msg":"你去aeon/一田應該有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢類盒裝既味增見過有好多種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2097b752f463c1b64d2cd5b9f4e43c0f77ae17","tid":398932,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:49:50.000Z","msg":"みそ咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8cc483a602da8831846ea2f368bd46ffc3df60","tid":398932,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T00:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好好食"},{"pid